Now the lever buster problem;
I love to play league of legends and i have spent lots of money on RP and other deals, but i have one problem i afk not because i want to but because i have(wont explain, personal) and i deserve the lever time thing(have to wait minutes for five games before going into a game) i have no problem with doing that because i deserve it. So recently i thought "well if i know i&#039;m going to have chance of afking, why don&#039;t i just play co-op that way i can still play lol and not ruin other peoples games hence i wont get punished" but i was wrong turns out lever buster works on co-op games!!!!

Riot can you please abolish the lever buster for co-op games. Remember co-op is a game against bots not humans so by me afking my team wont lose or suffer cause they are one player short.....
